# REQ-EXAMPLE-001: Application landing page is available

## Business purpose

A user can open the __APP_NAME__ landing page and recognize the application.

## Acceptance criteria

- The application URL is reachable.
- The landing-page title contains `__EXPECTED_TITLE__`.
- The main navigation is visible when navigation is part of the application layout.

## Out of scope

Application-specific infrastructure provisioning and authenticated behavior are defined by the consumer project.
